<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 yà bó lā hǎn xìn de shén, shì shǐ wú biàn wèi yǒu de shén,
 tā yě chéng le wǒ men zhōng guó rén de shén, yīn wèi tā tǒng guǎn quán qiú,
 yǐ yé hé huá wèi shén de nà gè guó, hái yǒu fú yǒu fú,
 wǒ men dōu chéng le méng ài de rén, méng tā de dà lián mǐn.
 shén zǎo yù dìng le zhōng guó rén, yào qǐ lái chuán fú yīn,
 huàn xǐng hān shuì chéng zhèn, jiān gù zhòng rén de xīn.
 hé děng dà de fú fèn, wǒ men yào shí shí gǎn ēn,
 tā cóng huáng tǔ zhōng tí liàn wǒ men de míng zì, chéng wèi tā yǒng yuǎn ài de rén.</lyrics>
<title>yà bó lā hǎn suǒ xìn de shén 迦南543</title>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>543</hymn_number>
</song>